      <title>麦吉尼斯称欧洲将推迟一年实施银行交易规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/europe-to-delay-bank-trading-rules-by-one-year-mcguinness-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将把全球银行资本规则的一个关键部分推迟一年实施，以便欧盟银行机构不会因美国标准持续争论而遭受不利影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/europe-to-delay-bank-trading-rules-by-one-year-mcguinness-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:52:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国十年期国债期货创收盘新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-10-year-bond-futures-see-record-close-amid-bull-run-lxk36470</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管受到当局的严格审查，但中国主权债券期货周二创下收盘新高，因国债购买狂潮仍在持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/china-s-10-year-bond-futures-see-record-close-amid-bull-run-lxk36470</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:31:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称法国成为欧洲最不受欢迎的股票市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/france-becomes-europe-s-least-preferred-stock-market-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行的一项调查显示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定提前举行大选，导致法国股票成为欧洲最不受欢迎的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/france-becomes-europe-s-least-preferred-stock-market-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:30:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙投票尘埃落定，欧洲股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/european-stocks-rebound-as-dust-settles-from-macron-vote-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市连续第二个交易日反弹，因投资者在大选前评估法国的政治发展，并在近期抛售后寻找机会，尽管涨幅仍然较小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/european-stocks-rebound-as-dust-settles-from-macron-vote-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 07:24:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
